{"tid":1173201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視劣勢當優勢 連發九貿戰新聞","createTime":"2019-05-27T03:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T06:08:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"13fdff4f83f25fd3632719f28179b6fb6bd7e4dd","tid":1173201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190527/20688266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F20688266&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=267d5edc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F20688266&h=ed73de8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190527/20688266</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n央視劣勢當優勢 連發九貿戰新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190527/large/a1402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190527%2Flarge%2Fa1402a.gif&h=658c86ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為研發的巴龍5000晶片。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰亦對美國企業造成損傷，美巨企微軟、通用電氣（GE）、Google母公司Alphabet等科技公司擔心，封殺華為可能阻礙企業在中國競爭，影響美國的創新能力。央視新聞聯播罕有連發九條有關中美貿易戰及創科新聞，借貿易促進會之口直斥美國的欺凌霸權，又指「中國企業應對經貿磨擦更為自信從容」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美媒揭「不擇手段」商業文化 華為偷呃拐騙歐美技術<br />\n<br />\n微軟通用電氣憂損創新力<br />\n<br />\n中國企業在貿易戰處在不利位置，多次被美國加徵關稅，但官方繼續在國內打輿論戰，昨天央視新聞聯播的15條新聞中，竟有9條與中美貿易戰或創科有關。官媒訪問了中國貿促會會長高燕，將劣勢說成優勢，顯示中國企業屹立不倒。她說：「中國企業在應對中美經貿磨擦中得到歷練，綜合競爭力、抗風險能力、開拓海外市場能力進一步提升，企業應對更為自信從容」，又指中國企業並非只有美國市場，能做到「東方不亮西方亮」。<br />\n<br />\n美國內部亦遇上一些擔憂，通用電氣關注在中國迅速發展的人工智能（AI），認為如果美對中國的出口管制範圍太闊，有可能影響開始使用的醫療成像（medical imaging）等技術。美國煙花行業現時亦感恐慌，美國95%的煙花產品都來自中國，每年進口到美國2.5億磅。俄亥俄州的幻影煙花（Phantom Fireworks）的行政總裁佐爾丹（Bruce Zoldan）說：「我們的產品幾乎不可能在中國以外的地方生產」。<br />\n<br />\n新華社/路透社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美媒揭「不擇手段」商業文化 華為偷呃拐騙歐美技術<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n新華社三記者疑刺探德軍情遭調查<br />\n<br />\n美媒揭「不擇手段」商業文化 華為偷呃拐騙歐美技術"},{"pid":"13f975cdc503adb01f4870178085aadb587064be","tid":1173201,"uid":9398,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"中共內聯網，最叻呃9國民洗佢地腦，白事當紅事辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f02f2c87cce5b9c45c64c8df8dc72e2062b218","tid":1173201,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"13f975cdc503adb01f4870178085aadb587064be","tid":1173201,"uid":9398,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"中共內聯網，最叻呃9國民洗佢地腦，白事當紅事辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"咁你明點解佢咁想控製香港傳媒啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e68e98610de56bb69358d4c574f2908f8b4992","tid":1173201,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"大難臨頭死不悔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518350d1d80a2e8290c69140cbb9d6ccedb75030","tid":1173201,"uid":183194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:25:22.000Z","msg":"勵害了我的國，永遠都是勝利者<br />\n<br />\n人民食樹皮也是最有營養的"},{"pid":"4c3da190a3eb99fadd9c4edbef5665551e45d167","tid":1173201,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國又成最大贏家</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202015-09-0320at2010.21.3